12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 67 O.S. 2021, Section 305, as
14 amended by Section 1, Chapter 189, O.S.L. 2022 (67 O.S. Supp. 2024,
15 Section 305), is amended to read as follows:
16 Section 305. There is hereby re-created until July 1, 2025
17 2028, in accordance with the Oklahoma Sunset Law, the Archives and
18 Records Commission, hereinafter referred to as the Commission, to be
19 composed of one member to be appointed by the Governor who shall
20 serve as Chairman, the State Librarian as Vice Chairman and
21 Secretary, the Lieutenant Governor, the State Auditor and Inspector
22 and the State Treasurer as members. Any member may appoint and
23 designate a subofficer or employee as his or her proxy for purposes
24 of carrying on the duties of the Commission. The Commission shall
